hadiths[72]{hadithnumber,text}:
4398,"Sufiyan-bin-Uena ne Zohri se, unhon-ne Umra se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) (soney ke) Dinar ke chauthey hissey ya us se zyada (ki maaliyat) mein chor ka hath kat-tey they."
4399,"Mamar, Sulaiman-bin Kasir aur Ibrahim bin Sad sab ne Zohri se isi sanad ke sath usi ki tarah hadis bayan ki."
4400,"ibne-Shahab ne Urwa aur Umra se, unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se aur unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke aap ne farmaya : (soney ke) Dinar ke chauthey hissey ya us se zyada (ki chori (ke siwa chor ka hath nahi kaata jaeyga"
4401,"Sulaiman-bin-Yasar ne Umra se riwayat ki ke unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se suna, wo bayan kar rahi thin ke unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : chothai Dinar ya us se zyada ke siwa hath nahi kaata jaeyga."
4402,"Abdul-Azeez bin-Muhammad ne Yazeed bin-Abdullah-bin haad se, unhon-ne Abu-Bakar bin-Muhammad se, unhon-ne Umra se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki ke unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : chothai Dinar ya us se zyada ke siwa chor ka hath nahi kaata jaeyga."
4403,Miswar-bin-Makhrama (Raziallahu anhu) ki aulad mein se Abdullah-bin Jafar ne Yazeed bin-Abdullah-bin haad se (baqi bachi) isi sanad ke sath usi ki tarah hadis bayan ki.
4404,"Muhammad-bin-Abdullah bin Numer ne kaha : Humaid bin Abdur-Rehman Ruwasi ne hamein Hisham-bin-Urwa se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne apne walid se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke ahad mein chor ka hath dhaal se kam maaliyat mein nahi kaata gaya, wo chamdey ki dhaal ho ya lohey ki, ye donon achi khasi qeemat wali thin. (maamooli cheez mein nahi kaata.)"
4405,"Abda bin Sulaiman, Humaid bin Abdur-Rehman, abdur-Raheem bin Sulaiman aur abu-Usama sab ne Hisham se isi sanad ke sath ibne-Numair ki Humaid se bayan ki hui riwayat ki tarah hadis bayan ki. aur abdur-Raheem aur abu-Usama ki hadis mein hai : un dinon wo ( dhaal ( qeemti cheez thi."
4406,"Yahya-bin-Yahya ne kaha : maine Imam Malik ke samney qirat ki, unhon-ne Naafe se aur unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne chor ka hath aik dhaal (ki chori) mein kaata jiski qeemat teen dirham thi."
4407,"Lais-bin-Sad, Ubaidullah (bin Umar-bin Hafs al-Umri), Ayub sakhtiyan, Ayub bin-Musa, Ismail bin Umayya, Musa-bin-Aqba, Hanzala bin abi Sufiyan jamhi, Ubaidullah-bin-Umar (Umri) Malik-bin-Anas aur Usama-bin-Zaid Lesi tak unke shagirdon ki mukhtalif sanadein hain. unke baad un sab ne Naafe se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se, Imam Malik se Yahya ki hadis ki tarah riwayat ki, albatta unmein se kuchh ne uski qeemat kaha aur kuchh ne teen dirham ka saman (mana wahi hai.)"
4408,"abu-Muawia ne Aamash se, unhon-ne Abu-Saleh se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Allah chor par laanat karey, wo anda charaataa hai to uska hath kat-taa hai aur rassi churaata hai to uska hath kat-taa hai."
4409,"Esa-bin-Yonus ne Aamash se isi sanad ke sath usi ki tarah hadis bayan ki, albatta wo kehtey hain : wo chahe rassi churaaey, chahe anda churaaey."
4410,"Qutaiba-bin-Saeed aur Muhammad-bin-Rumeh ne kaha : hamein Leis ne ibne-Shahab se khabar di, unhon-ne Urwa se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki ke Quraish ko aik makhzumi aurat , jisne chori ki thi, ke mamley ne fikr mand kar diya, unhon-ne kaha : iske barey mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se kon baat karega? kehney lagey : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke piyarey Hazrat Usama (Raziallahu anhu) hi uski jur'at kar saktey hain? chunanche Hazrat Usama (Raziallahu anhu) ne aap se guftgu ki to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : kya tum hudood Allah main se aik had (ko saaqit (khatm) karne) ke barey mein sifarish kar rahe ho? phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) uthey , khutba diya aur farmaya : aey logo ! tum se pahley logon ko isi cheez ne tabah kar daala ke jab unka koi muazziz (apna khas) aadmi chori karta to usey chhod detey aur jab unmein se koi kamzor aadmi chori karta to is par had Nafiz (laagu) kartey. Allah ki qism ! agar Fatima-binte- Muhammad bhi chori karti to main uska hath bhi kaat deta. ibne- Rumeh ki hadis mein : tum se pahley log tabah ho gaey ke alfaz hain."
4411,"Younus-bin-Yazeed ne mujhey ibne-Shahab se khabar di, unhon-ne kaha : mujhey Urwa-bin-Zubair ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki bevi mohtarma Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se khabar di ke Quraish ko us aurat ke mamley ne fikr mand kiya jisne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke ahad mein, jange-fatah Makka (ke dinon) mein chori ki thi. unhon-ne kaha : uske barey mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se kon baat karega? (kuchh) logon ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke chaheetey Usama-bin-Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) hi uski jur'at kar saktey hain. wo aurat Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke samney pesh ki gaee to Hazrat Usama-bin-Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) ne uske barey mein baat ki, is par Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke chehre Mubarak ka rang badal gaya aur farmaya : kya tum Allah ki hudood mein se aik had ke barey mein sifarish kar rahe ho? to Hazrat Usama (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : Allah ke rasool ! mere liye maghfirat talab kijiye. jab Sham ka waqt hua to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) uthey , khutba diya, Allah ke shaayaan shaan uski sana bayan ki, phir farmaya : amma'baad ! tum se pahley logon ko isi cheez ne halaak kar daala ke jab unmein se koi apna insan chori karta to wo usey chhod detey aur jab kamzor chori karta to is par had Nafiz kar detey. aur main, us zaat ki qism jiske hath mein meri jaan hai ! agar Fatima binte-Muhammad bhi chori karti to uska (bhi) hath kaat deta. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us aurat ke barey mein hukm diya jisne chori ki thi to uska hath kaat diya gaya. Yunus ne kaha : ibne-Shahab ne kaha : Urwa ne kaha : Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha : iske baad uski tauba (Allah ki taraf tawajjoh bahu ( achi (ho gai) aur us ne shadi kar li aur uske baad wo mere paas aati thi to main uski zarurat Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke samney pesh karti thi."
4412,"Mamar ne Zohri se, unhon-ne Urwa se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : banu-makhzoom ki aik aurat aariyatan (udhar) saman leti thi aur phir uska inkar kar diya karti thi. (phir us ne chori kar dali) to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne uska hath kaatney ka hukm diya. is par iske ghar waley Hazrat Usama-bin-Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas aaey aur unse baat ki to unhon-ne is silsiley mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se baat ki, phir Leis aur Yunus ki hadis ki tarah bayan kiya."
4413,"Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke banu-makhzoom ki aik aurat ne chori ki, usey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke samney laya gaya to usne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki bevi mohtarma Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) ki panah li to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : agar Fatima (binte- Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bhi) hoti to main uska hath kaat deta. chunanche us aurat ka hath kaat diya gaya."
4414,"Yahya-bin-Yahya tamimi ne kaha : Hushaim ne hamein Mansoor se khabar di, unhon-ne Hasan se, unhon-ne Hittan-bin-Abdullah Raqashi se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Ubada-bin-Samit (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : mujh se seekh lo, mujh se seekh lo, mujh se seekh lo (jis tarah Allah ne farmaya tha : ya Allah unke liye koi raah nikaley. ( Nisa : 15 : 4 ( Allah ne unke liye raah nikaali hai, kunwara , kunwari se (zina karey) to (har aik ke liye) so kode aur aik saal ki jilaa watani hai aur shadi shuda se zina karey to (har aik ke liye) so kode aur rajm (sangsaar) hai."
4415,"Amr Naqid ne kaha : hamein Hushaim ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Mansoor ne isi sanad ke sath usi ki tarah khabar di."
4416,"Saeed ne Qatada se, unhon-ne Hasan se, unhon-ne Hittan-bin-Abdullah Raqashi se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Ubada-bin-Samit (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) par jab wahi nazil ki jati to aap par uski wjah se takleef (ki kaifiyat ( taari ho jati thi aur aap ke chehrey ka rang tabdeel ho jata tha, kaha : aik din aap par wahi nazil ki gaee to aap usi kaifiyat se do-chaar huey. jab aap se ye kaifiyat door hui to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : mujh se seekh lo, Allah ne un (aurton) ke liye raah nikal di hai, shadi shuda , shadi shuda se (zina karey) aur kunwaaraa , kunwari se (ya kunwaaraa shadi shuda se to ( shadi shuda ke liye (saza) so kode , phir pattharon se rajm (sangsaar) karna hai aur kunwaarey ke liye so kode phir aik saal ki jilaa watani hai."
4417,"Shoba aur Hisham ne Qatada se isi sanad ke sath hadis bayan ki, albatta un donon ki hadis mein hai : kunwaarey ko kode lagaey jaeinge aur jilaa watan kiya jaeyga aur shadi shuda ko kode lagaey jaeinge aur rajm (sangsaar) kiya jaeyga. un donon ne ( jilaa watani ke liye) aik saal aur) kodon ke liye) aik sau ka tazkira nahi kiya."
4418,"Yunus ne mujhey ibne-Shahab se khabar di, unhon-ne kaha : mujhey Ubaidullah-bin-Abdullaah-bin-Utba ne khabar di ke unhon-ne Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo keh rahe they : Hazrat Umar-bin-Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha, aur wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke member par tashrif farma they : bila shubah Allah Taala ne Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko haq ke sath maboos kiya (bheja) aur aap par kitab nazil farmai, Allah ne aap par jo nazil kiya usmein rajm (sangsaar) ki aayat bhi thi, ham ne usey padha , yad kiya aur samjha , isliye Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne bhi rajm (sangsaar) ki saza di aur aap ke baad ham ne bhi rajm (sangsaar) ki saza di, mujhey dar hai ke logon par aik lamba zamana guzar jaeyga to koi kehney wala kahega : ham Allah ki kitab mein rajm (sangsaar) (ka hukm ( nahi patey, to wo log aisey farz ko chhodney se gumrah ho jaeinge. jisey Allah ne nazil kiya hai aur bila shubah Allah ki kitab mein rajm (sangsaar) (ka hukm ( aurton aur mardon mein se har aik par jisne zina kiya, jab wo shadi shuda ho, bar-haq hai. (ye saza us waqt di jaeygi) jab shahadat qaaim ho jaey ya hamal thahar jaey ya (zaani ki taraf se) aetiraaf ho."
4419,Sufiyan ne Zohri se isi sanad ke sath hadis bayan ki.
4420,"Aqeel (bin-Khalid-umwi) ne ibne-Shahab se, unhon-ne abu-Salma-bin-Abdur-Rehmaan-bin-Auf aur Saeed-bin-Musaiyab se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke unhon-ne kaha : musalmanon mein se aik aadmi Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aaya, aap masjid mein tashrif farma they, us ne aapko awaz di aur kaha : aey Allah ke rasool ! maine zina kiya hai. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne uski taraf se munh pher liya, wo ghoom kar aik taraf se aap ke samney aaya aur kehney laga : Allah ke rasool ! maine zina kiya hai. aap ne (phir) us se munh phir liya yahan tak ke usne aap ke samney yahi kalimaat char martaba dohraaey. jab us ne apne khilaf char gawahiyan dein to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne usey bulaya aur puchha : kya tumhen junoon hai? usne kaha : nahi. aap ne puchha : kya tum ne shadi ki hai? usne kaha : ji haan. to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : isey ley jao aur rajm (sangsaar) karo. ibne-Shahab ne kaha : mujhey is aadmi ne bataya jisne Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se ye hadis suni thi, wo keh rahe they : main bhi un logon mein tha jinhoney usey rajm (sangsaar) kiya, ham ne usey janaaza gaah mein rajm (sangsaar) kiya tha. jab pattharon ne uski bardasht khatm kar di to wo bhag nikla, ham ne usey siyah pattharon wali zamin mein ja liya aur rajm (sangsaar) kar diya."
4421,Abdur-Rehman-bin-Khalid-bin-musaafir ne ibne-Shahab se isi sanad ke sath usi ki tarah hadis bayan ki.
4422,Shuaib ne bhi Zohri se isi sanad ke sath khabar di aur un donon (Abdur-Rehman-bin-Khalid-bin-musaafir aur Shuaib) ki hadis mein hai : ibne-Shahab ne kaha : mujhey us shakhs ne bataya jisne Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se suna. isi tarah jaisey Aqeel ne hadis bayan ki.
4423,"Yunus , Mamar aur ibne-Juraij sab ne Zohri se, unhon-ne abu-Salma se, unhon-ne Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se isi tarah riwayat bayan ki jis tarah Aqeel ne Zohri se. unhon-ne Saeed (bin-Musaiyab (aur abu-Salma (bin-Abdur-Rehman-bin-Auf ( se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki."
4424,"abu-Awana ne Samak-bin-Harab se, unhon-ne Hazrat Jaabir-bin-Samra (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine maaiz-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ko , jab wo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke samney pesh kiye gaey, dekha, wo chhotey qad ke mazbut putthon waley aadmi they, un par koi chadar nahi thi. unhon-ne apne khilaf char martaba gawahi di ke unhon-ne zina kiya hai. to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : shayad tum ne (kuchh aur maslan : bossa aur kinaar kiya hoga) unhon-ne kaha : nahi, Allah ki qism ! is bad-bakht ne zina (hi) kiya hai. kaha : aap ne usey rajm (sangsaar) karne ka hukm diya, phir khutba diya aur farmaya : suno , jab ham Allah ki raah mein jihad ke liye nikaltey hain to un logon mein se koi peechhey reh jata hai, wo nasl kushi ke bakrey ki tarah josh se aawazein nikalta hai aur (aurton ko aamada karne ke liye) mamooli cheez pesh karta hai. suno ! Allah ki qism ! agar us ne mujhey unmein se kisi aik ko) saboot samet ( mere qaabu mein diya to main usko ibratnaak (khaufnak) saza doonga ."
4425,"Muhammad-bin-Jafar ne kaha : hamein Shoba ne Samak-bin-Harab se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine Hazrat Jaabir-bin-Samra (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas chhotey qad , bikhrey huey baalon aur mazbut putthon wala aik shakhs laya gaya, us (ke jism ( par aik tehband tha aur us ne zina ka irtikaab kiya tha. aap ne usey dobara lautaaya, phir usey (rajm (sangsaar) karne ka ( hukm diya to usey rajm (sangsaar) kar diya gaya, iske baad Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ( khutba detey huey) farmaya : ham jab bhi Allah ki raah mein jihad ke liye nikaltey hain to tum logon mein se koi shakhs peechhey reh jata hai. wo nasl-kushi ke bakrey ki tarah josh se aawaazein nikalta hai aur aurton mein se kisi ko) aamada karne ke liye) mamooli si cheez pesh karta hai. bila shubah Allah jab bhi mujhey unmein se kisi aik par qaabu dega to main laziman usey ( logon ke liye) ibrat bana doonga. ya ibratnaak saza doonga . kaha : maine ye hadis Saeed-bin-Jubair ko bayan ki to unhon-ne kaha : aap ne usey char baar wapas kiya tha."
4426,"Shababaa aur abu-Aamir aqadi donon ne Shoba se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Samak se, unhon-ne Hazrat Jabir-bin-Samra (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se ibne-Jafar ki hadis ki tarah riwayat ki aur Shababaa ne is baat mein unki muwafiqat (barabri) ki ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne usey do baar lautaya aur abu-Aamir ki hadis mein hai : aap ne usey do ya teen baar wapas kiya."
4427,"Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ( char baar wapas karne aur uske israar ke baad) maaiz-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se puchha : kya wo baat sach hai jo mujhey tumharey barey mein pahunchi hai? unhon-ne kaha : mere barey mein aapko kya baat pahunchi hai? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : mujhey ye baat pahunchi hai ke tum ne falan khandan ki londi se zina kiya hai. unhon-ne kaha : ji haan. kaha : to unhon-ne (apne khilaf ( char gawahiyan dein, phir aap ne un (ko rajm (sangsaar) karne) ke barey mein hukm diya to unhein rajm (sangsaar) kar diya gaya."
4428,"Abdul-Aala ne kaha : hamein Dawud ne abu-Nazara se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Hazrat abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Aslam qabeeley ka aik aadmi, jisey maaiz-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) kaha jata tha. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aaya aur kaha : mujh se badkaari ho gaee hai, mujh par uski had Nafiz (laagu) kijiye. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne usey kai baar wapas kiya. kaha : phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne uski qaum se puchha to unhon-ne kaha : ham unki kisi burai ko nahi jaantey, magar unse koi baat sarzad zaroor hui hai. ham samajhtey hain ke unhein is kaifiyat se, iske ilawa aur koi cheez nahi nikal sakti ke un par had qaaim kar di jaey. kaha : iske baad wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas phir wapas aaey to aap ne hamein hukm diya ke unhein rajm (sangsaar) kar dein. kaha : ham unhein Baqee-algharqad ki taraf lekar gaey. kaha : na ham ne unhein baandha, na unke liye garhaa khoda . kaha : ham ne unhein haddiyon , mitti ke dhelon aur theekron se maara . kaha : wo bhag nikley to ham bhi unke peechhey bhaagey yahan tak ke wo Harra ( siyah pattharon wali zamin (ke aik kinarey par aaey aur hamarey samney jam kar khadey ho gaey. phir ham ne unhein Harra ki chattaanon ke tukdon , yani (badey-badey) pattharon se mara yahan tak ke wo be jaan ho gaey, kaha : phir Sham ko Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) khutba dene ke liye khadey huey aur farmaya : jab bhi ham Allah ki raah mein jihad karne ke liye nikaltey hain koi aadmi peechhey hamarey ahal aur ayaal ke darmyan reh jata hai aur bakrey ki tarah josh mein aawaazein nikaalta hai, mujh par lazim hai ke mere paas koi aisa aadmi nahi laya jaeyga jisne aisa kiya hoga magar main usey ibratnaak saza doonga . kaha : Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ( khutbey ke doran mein) na unke liye istighfar kiya, na unhein bura bhala kaha."
4429,"Yazeed-bin-Zuree ne kaha : hamein Dawud ne isi sanad ke sath usi ke ham mana hadis bayan ki aur unhon-ne hadis mein kaha : Sham ko Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) khadey huey, Allah ki hamd aur sana bayan ki, phir farmaya : amaa-baad ! logon ka kya haal hai? jab ham jihad ke liye jatey hain to unmein se koi shakhs peechhey reh jata hai, wo nasl kushi ke bakrey ki tarah aawazein nikaltaa hai. unhon ( Yazeed-bin-Zuree ( ne hamarey ahal aur ayaal mein ke alfaz nahi kahey."
4430,"Yahya-bin-Zakariya-bin-abi-Zayda aur Sufiyan donon ne Dawud se isi sanad ke sath us hadis ka kuchh hissey bayan kiya, albatta Sufiyan ki hadis mein hai is ne teen baar zina ka aetiraaf kiya. ( chauthi baar ke aetraaf par usey saza sunai gaee.)"
4431,"Sulaiman-bin-Barida ne apne walid ( Barida-bin-Hasib Aslami (Raziallahu anhu)) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : maaiz-bin-Malik ( Aslami ( (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aaey aur kehney lagey : aey Allah ke rasool ! mujhey paak kijiye . Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : tum par afsos ! jao, Allah se istighfar karo aur uski bargah mein tauba karo. kaha : wo lot kar thodi door tak gaey, phir wapas aaey aur kehney lagey : aey Allah ke rasool ! mujhey paak kijiye . to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : tum par afsos ! jao, Allah se istighfar karo aur uski taraf rujoo karo. kaha : wo lot kar thodi door tak gaey, phir aaey aur kehney lagey : aey Allah ke rasool ! mujhey paak kijiye. to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ( phir ( isi tarah farmaya yahan tak ke jab chauthi baar ( yahi baat ( hui, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us se puchha : main tumhen kis cheez se paak karun? unhon-ne kaha : zina se. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne puchha : kya usey junoon hai? to aapko bataya gaya ke ye majnoon nahi hai. to aap ne puchha : kya usne sharab pi hai? is par aik aadmi khada hua aur uska munh soonghaa to usey us se sharab ki bo na aai. kaha : to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne puchha : kya tum ne zina kiya hai? unhon-ne jawab diya : ji haan ( yahin aap ne us se us waqiey ki tasdeeq chahi jo aap tak pahuncha tha) phir aap ne un (ko rajm (sangsaar) karne) ke barey mein hukm diya. chunanche unhein rajm (sangsaar) kar diya gaya. baad iske unke hawale se logon ke do giroh bin gaey, kuchh kehney waley ye kehtey : wo tabah aur barbad ho gaya, uske gunah ne usey gher liya aur kuchh kehney waley ye kehtey : Maaiz (Raziallahu anhu) ki tauba se afzal koi tauba nahi (ho sakti) ke wo (khud) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aaey aur aap ke hath mein apna hath diya, phir kaha : mujhey pattharon se mar daaliye . kaha : do ya teen din wo (ikhtilaf ki) usi kaifiyat mein rahe, phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tashrif laaey. wo sab baithey huey they, aap ne salam kaha, phir baith gaey aur farmaya : maaiz-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ke liye bakhshish maango. kaha : to logon ne kaha : Allah maaiz-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ko maaf farmaai ! to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : bila shubah unhon-ne aisi tauba ki hai ke agar wo aik ummat mein baant di jaey to un sab ko kafi ho jaey. kaha : phir aap ke paas Azd qabeeley ki shaakh ghaamid ki aik aurat aai aur kehney lagi : Allah ke rasool ! mujhey paak kijiye. to aap ne farmaya : tum par afsos ! lot jao, Allah se bakhshish maango aur uski taraf rujoo karo. usne kaha : mera khayal hai aap mujhey bhi baar-baar lautana chahtey hain jaisey maaiz-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ko lautaya tha. aap ne puchha : wo kya baat hai (jis main tum tatheer (paki) chahti ho? ( usne kaha : wo zina ki wjah se haamla hai. to aap ne (taakeedan) puchha : kya tum khud ? us ne jawab diya : ji haan , to aap ne usey farmaya : (jaao) yahan tak ke jo tumharey pet mein hai usey janm de do. kaha : to Ansar ke aik aadmi ne uski kifaalat ki yahan tak ke usne bachchey ko janm diya. kaha : to wo aadmi Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur kehney laga : ghaamidi aurat ne bachchey ko janm de diya hai. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : tab ham (abhi) usey rajm (sangsaar) nahi karengey aur uske bachchey ko kam umr mein (is tarah) nahi chhodengey ke koi usey doodh pilaaney wala na ho. phir Ansar ka aik aadmi khada hua aur kaha : aey Allah ke Nabi ! uski razaat (doodh pilana) mere zimmey hai. kaha : to aap ne usey rajm (sangsaar) karne ka hukm de diya."
4432,"bushair-bin-muhajir ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : Abdullah-bin-Barida ne hamein apne walid se hadis bayan ki ke maaiz-bin-Malik Aslami (Raziallahu anhu) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aaey aur kaha : aey Allah ke rasool ! maine apni jaan par zulm kiya hai, maine zina ka irtikaab kiya hai aur main chahta hun ke aap mujhey ( gunah ki aaloodgi se) paak kar dein. aap ne unhein wapas bhej diya, jab aglaa din hua, wo aap ke paas aaey aur kaha : aey Allah ke rasool ! maine zina kiya hai. to aap ne dusri baar unhein wapas bhej diya. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unki qaum ki taraf paigham bheja aur puchha : kya tum jantey ho ke unki aql mein koi kharabi hai, (unke amal mein) tumhen koi cheez ghalat lagti hai? to unhon-ne jawab diya : hamarey ilm main to ye poori aql waley hain, jahan tak hamara khayal hai. ye hamarey Saleh (nek) afraad mein se hain. wo aap ke paas teesri baar aaey to aap ne phir unki taraf (usi tarah) paigham bheja aur unke barey mein puchha to unhon-ne bataya ke unmein aur unki aql mein koi kharabi nahi hai, jab chothi baar aisa hua to aap ne unke liye aik garhaa khudwaya , phir un (ko rajm (sangsaar) karne) ke barey mein hukm diya to unhein rajm (sangsaar) kar diya gaya. kaha : iske baad ghaamid qabeeley ki aurat aai aur kehney lagi : aey Allah ke rasool ! maine zina kiya hai, mujhey paak kijiye . aap ne usey wapas bhej diya, jab aglaa din hua, usne kaha : aey Allah ke rasool ! aap mujhey wapas kyon bhejtey hain? shayad aap mujhey bhi isi tarah wapas bhejna chahtey hain jaisey Maaiz (Raziallahu anhu) ko bheja tha. Allah ki qism ! main hamal se hun. aap ne farmaya : agar nahi (maanti ho) to jao yahan tak ke tum bachchey ko janm de do. kaha : jab us ne usey janm diya to bachchey ko aik boseeda kapdey ke tukdey mein lekar aap ki khidmat mein hazir hui aur kaha : ye hai, maine usko janm de diya hai. aap ne farmaya : jao, usey doodh pilaaw yahan tak ke tum iska doodh chhudaa do. jab us ne uska doodh chhudaa diya to bachchey ko lekar aap ke paas hazir hui, uske hath mein roti ka tukda tha, usne kaha : aey Allah ke Nabi ! maine iska doodh chhudaa diya hai aur us ne khana bhi kha liya hai. ( abhi uski muddat razaat (doodh pilane ki) baqi thi. aik Ansari ne uski zimme-dari utha li) to aap ne bachcha musalmanon mein se aik aadmi (is Ansari (ke hawale kiya, phir uske liye ( garhaa khodney ka ( hukm diya to seeney tak uske liye garhaa khodaa gaya aur aap ne logon ko hukm diya to unhon-ne usey rajm (sangsaar) kar diya. Hazrat Khalid-bin-Waleed (Raziallahu anhu) aik patthar lekar aagey badhey aur uske sar par maara , khoon ka fawwaara phoot kar Hazrat Khalid (Raziallahu anhu) ke chehrey par padaa to unhon-ne usey bura bhala kaha. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unke bura bhala kehney ko sun liya to aap ne farmaya : Khalid ! thahar jao, us zaat ki qism jiske hath mein meri jaan hai ! us aurat ne aisi tauba ki hai ke agar naajaaiz mahsool (tex) leney wala (jo zulm ke sath laa-taadaad insanon ka haq khata hai) aisi tauba karey to usey bhi maaf kar diya jaey. phir aap ne iske barey mein hukm diya aur uski namaaze-janaaza padhai aur usey dafn kar diya gaya."
4433,"Hisham ne mujhey Yahya-bin-abi-Kasir se hadis bayan ki, kaha : mujhey abu-Qilaba ne hadis bayan ki ke unhein abu-Mohlab ne Hazrat Imran-bin-Husain (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis bayan ki ke qabila juhaina ki aik aurat Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aai , wo zina se haamla thi, usne kaha : Allah ke rasool ! main (sharaee) had ki mustahiq ho gaee hun, aap wo had mujh par Nafiz (laagu) farmaein. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne uske wali ko bulwaya aur farmaya : iske sath achchha sulook karo, jab ye bachchey ko janm de to usey mere paas ley aana . us ne aisa hi kiya. phir Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne uske barey mein hukm diya to uske kapdey is par kas kar baandh diye gaey, phir aap ne hukm diya to usey rajm (sangsaar) kar diya gaya, phir aap ne uski namaaze-janaaza padhai. to Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne aap se kaha : Allah ke Nabi ! aap uski namaaze-janaaza padhaaeingey halanke us ne zina kiya hai? aap ne farmaya is ne yaqinan aisi tauba ki hai ke agar ahale-Madina ke  sattar (70) gharon ke darmyan taqseem kar di jaey to unke liye bhi kafi ho jaeygi aur kya tum ne us se behtar (koi) tauba dekhi hai? ke usne Allah (ko razi karne) ke liye apni jaan qurbaan kar di hai."
4434,Aban attaar ne Yahya-bin-abi-Kasir se isi sanad ke sath usi ki tarah hadis bayan ki.
4435,"Leis ne ibne-Shahab se, unhon-ne Ubaidullah-bin-Abdullah-bin-Utba-bin-Masood se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera aur Hazrat Zaid-bin-Khalid Juhni (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke un donon ne kaha : baadiya nasheen (jangal ke rehne wale) mein se aik aadmi Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aaya aur kehney laga : aey Allah ke rasool ! main aapko Allah ki qism deta hun, aap mere liye Allah ki kitab ke mutabiq faisla karein. (iske ( mukhalif fareeq ne kaha : aur wo us se zyada samajh daar tha, ji haan , hamarey darmyan Allah ki kitab ki taraf se faisla kijiye aur mujhey ( kuchh kehney ki) ijazat dijiye. to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : kaho. usne kaha : mera betaa iske yahaan mazdoor tha, us ne iski biwi se zina kiya aur mujhey bataya gaya ke mere betey par rajm (sangsaar) (ki saza) hai, chunanche maine uski taraf se aik sau bakriyan aur aik londi bataur fidya di, aur ahale-ilm se puchha to unhon-ne mujhey bataya hai ke mere betey par (to) aik sau kode aur aik saal ki jilaa watani hai aur rajm (sangsaar) uski aurat par hai. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya is zaat ki qism jiske hath mein meri jaan hai ! main tumharey darmyan Allah ki kitab ke mutabiq faisla karunga, londi aur bakriyan tujhey wapas milein gi, tumharey betey par aik sau kode aur aik saal ki jilaa watani hai. unnais ! ( Anas-bin-zuhhak Aslami (Raziallahu anhu) murad hain. aurat unhi ke qabeeley se thi) us (doosrey aadmi) ki aurat ke yahan jao, agar wo aetiraaf karey to usey rajm (sangsaar) kar do. kaha : wo iske yahaan gaey to usne aetiraaf kar liya, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us (ko rajm (sangsaar) karne) ka hukm diya, chunanche usey rajm (sangsaar) kar diya gaya."
4436,"Yunus , Saleh aur Mamar sab ne Zohri se isi sanad ke sath isi tarah hadis bayan ki."
4437,"Ubaidullah ne hamein Naafe se khabar di, kaha : Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne unhein bataya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aik Yahudi mard aur aik Yahudi aurat ko laya gaya jinhoney zina kiya tha, to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) chal padey yahan tak ke yahood ke paas aaey aur puchha : tum tauraat mein is aadmi ke barey mein kya saza patey ho jisne zina kya ho? unhon-ne kaha : ham un donon ka munh kala kartey hain, unhein (gadhey par) sawar kartey hain, un donon ke chehrey mukhalif samt mein kar detey hain aur unhein (galiyon bazaron mein) phiraayaa jata hai. aap ne farmaya : agar tum sachey ho, tauraat ley aao. wo usey laey aur padhney lagey yahan tak ke jab rajm (sangsaar) ki aayat ke nazdeek pahunchey to us naujawaan ne, jo padh raha tha, apna hath rajm (sangsaar) ki aayat par rakha aur wo hissey padh diya jo aagey tha aur jo peechhey tha. is par Hazrat Abdullaah-bin-Salaam (Raziallahu anhu) ne aap se arz ki, aur wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath maujood they, aap usey hukm dijiye ki apna hath uthaey . us ne hath uthaya to iske nichey rajm (sangsaar) ki aayat (maujood ( thi, is par Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne un donon (ko rajm (sangsaar) karne) ka hukm saadir farmaya to unhein rajm (sangsaar) kar diya gaya. Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : main bhi un logon mein tha jinhoney unhein rajm (sangsaar) kiya, maine us aadmi ko dekha wo apne ( jism ke) zariey se us aurat ko bacha raha tha."
4438,"ibne-Ulaih ne hamein Ayub se khabar di, neez (isi ke sath) Abdullah-bin-Wahab ne kaha : mujhey ahale-ilm mein se bahut se aadmiyon ne jin mein imam Malik-bin-Anas (Rehmatullahi-alaih) bhi shamil hain, khabar di ke unhein Naafe ne bataya , unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne zina (ki had) mein do yahudiyon , aik mard aur aik aurat ko , jinhoney zina kiya tha, rajm (sangsaar) karaya. yahood unhein lekar Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aaey they. aagey usi (pichhli hadis ki) tarah hadis bayan ki."
4439,"Musa-bin-Aqba ne hamein Naafe se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke yahood apne aik mard aur aik aurat ko , jinhoney zina kiya tha, lekar Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aaey. padhi. aagey Naafe se Ubaidullah ki riwayat ki hui hadis ki tarah bayan kiya."
4440,"abu-Muawiya ne Aamash se, unhon-ne Abdullah-bin-Murra se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Bara-bin-Aazib (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : aik Yahudi ko Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke qareeb se guzara gaya jiska munh kala kiya hua tha usey kode lagaey gaey they, aap ne unhein (unke aalimon ko) bulaya aur puchha : kya tum apni kitab mein zaani ki had isi tarah patey ho? unhon-ne kaha : ji haan. (baad iske aap ke hukm se Taurait mangwaai gaee. unhon-ne aayat rajm (sangsaar) chipa li, wo zahir ho gaee. iske baad aap ne unke ulma mein se aik aadmi ko bulaya aur farmaya : main tumhen us Allah ki qism deta hun jisne Musa (Alaihissalam) par Taurait nazil ki ! kya tum log apni kitab mein zaani ki had isi tarah patey ho? us ne jawab diya : nahi, aur agar aap mujhey ye qism na detey to main aapko na bataataa. (ham kitab mein) rajm (sangsaar) (ki saza likhi hui ( patey hain. lekin hamarey ashraaf mein zina bahut badh gaya. (is wjah se) ham jab kisi muazziz (apne) ko pakadtey they, to usey chhod detey they aur jab kisi kamzor ko pakadtey to is par had Nafiz kar detey they. ham ne (aapas mein) kaha : aao ! kisi aisi cheez (saza) par jama ho jayen jisey ham muazziz aur maamooli aadmi (donon) par laagu kar sakein, to ham ne rajm (sangsaar) ke bajaey munh kala karne aur kode lagaaney (ki saza ( bana li. is par Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : aey Allah ! main wo pahlaa shakhs hun jisne terey hukm ko zinda kiya jabke unhon-ne usey murda kar diya tha. phir aap ne uske barey mein hukm diya to usey rajm (sangsaar) kar diya gaya. is par izzat aur jalaal waaley Allah ne (ye aayat ( nazil farmai : aey rasool ! aap un logon ke peechhey na khadhey jo tezi se kufr mein dakhil hotey hain. is farman tak : agar tumhen yahi hukm diya jaey to qabool kar lenaa. ( Mayeda : 41 : 5 ( ) unko mashwara dene wala ( kehta tha : Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas jao, agar wo tumhen ( yahi ( munh kala karne aur kode lagaaney ka hukm dein to qabool kar lena aur agar rajm (sangsaar) ka fatwa dein to ehtiraaz karna. is par Allah Taala ne (ye aayat ( nazil farmai : aur jo log us ( hukm (ke mutabiq faisla na karein jo Allah ne nazil kiya hai to wahi log kaafir hain. ( Mayeda : 44 : 5 (aur jo iske mutabiq faisla na karein jo Allah ne nazil kiya hai to wahi log zaalim hain. ( المائدۃ : 45 : 5 (aur jo iske mutabiq faisla na karein jo Allah ne utara hai to wahi log fasiq hain. ( Mayeda : 47 : 5 ( ye saari aayatein kuffaar ke barey mein hain."
4441,"Wakee ne hamein hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Aamash ne isi sanad ke sath us qaul tak , isi tarah hadis bayan ki : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hukm diya to usey rajm (sangsaar) kar diya gaya. unhon-ne iske baad ka, aayaton ke nazil honey wala hissey bayan nahi kiya."
4442,"Hujjaj-bin-Muhammad ne hamein hadis bayan ki, kaha : ibne-Juraij ne kaha : mujhey abu-Zubair ne khabar di ke unhon-ne Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ko ye kehtey huey suna : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne qabila Aslam ke aik mard aur yahood ke aik mard aur uski ( aashnaa/jankar ( aurat ko rajm (sangsaar) karwaya."
4443,"Rauh-bin-Ubada ne ibne-Juraij se isi sanad ke sath usi ki tarah hadis bayan ki, albatta unhon-ne (aur uski aurat ke bajaey sirf (aur aurat kaha."
4444,"Abu-Ishaq Shebani se riwayat hai, unhon-ne kaha : maine Abdullah-bin-abi-Ufa (Raziallahu anhu) se puchha : kya Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne rajm (sangsaar) kiya? unhon-ne kaha : haan. kaha : maine puchha : sura noor nazil kiye janey ke baad ya us se pahley ? unhon-ne kaha : main nahi janta."
4445,"Leis ne Saeed-bin-abi-Saeed se, unhon-ne apne walid se khabar di, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne unhein ( Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu)) ye kehtey huey suna ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, aap farma rahe they : jab tum mein se kisi ki londi zina karey aur uska zina ( kisi daleel se) waazeh ( Sabit (ho jaey to wo ( Malik ( is par had lagaey aur usey malaamat na karta rahe, phir agar wo zina karey to usko had lagaey aur usey malaamat na karta rahe, phir agar wo teesri baar zina karey aur uska zina waazeh ho jaey to usey farokht kar de, chahey baalon ki aik rassi hi ke iwaz kyon na bikey."
4446,"Ayub-bin-Musa , Ubaidullah-bin-Umar , Usama-bin-Zaid aur Muhammad-bin-Ishaq sab ne Saeed Maqbari se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki, albatta ibne-Ishaq ne apni hadis mein kaha : Saeed ne apne walid se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se londi ko , jab wo teen baar zina karey, kode lagaaney ki baat riwayat ki, ( aagey farmaya ( phir chothi baar usey farokht kar de."
4447,"Abdullaah-bin-Muslima Qanabi ne kaha : hamein Malik ne hadis sunai, aur Yahya-bin-Yahya ne. padhi. hadis ke alfaz unhi ke hain. padhi. kaha : maine Imam Malik ke samney qirat ki, unhon-ne ibne-Shahab se, unhon-ne Ubaidullah-bin-Abdullah se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se londi ke barey mein puchha gaya, jab wo zina karey aur shadi shuda na ho, to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : agar wo zina karey to usey kode lagaao , phir agar zina karey to usey kode lagaao , phir usey farokht kar do, chahey aik gundhi hui rassi ke iwaz kyon na ho. ibne-Shahab ne kaha : main nahi janta ye ( bechney ka hukm ( teesri baar ke baad hai ya chothi baar ke baad . Qanabi ne apni riwayat mein kaha : ibne-Shahab ne kaha : aur zafeer se murad rassi hai."
4448,"ibne- Wahab ne kaha : maine Imam Malik se suna, wo keh rahe they : mujhey ibne-Shahab ne Ubaidullah-bin-Abdullaah-bin-Utba se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera aur Zaid-bin-Khalid Juhni (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se londi ke barey mein puchha gaya. padhi. jis tarah un donon ki hadis hai. aur unhon-ne ibne-Shahab ke qaul : zafeer se murad rassi hai ka tazkira nahi kiya."
4449,"Saleh aur Mamar donon ne Zohri se, unhon-ne Ubaidullah se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera aur Hazrat Zaid-bin-Khalid Juhni (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki, jis tarah Imam Malik ki hadis hai. aur uska Sauda teesri baar hai ya chothi baar , usmein shak donon ki hadis mein hai."
4450,"Zayda ne suddi se, unhon-ne Sad-bin-ubaida se aur unhon-ne abu-Abdur-Rehman se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Hazrat Ali karam Allah wajha ne khutba diya aur kaha : aey logo ! apne ghulaamon par had Nafiz karo, jo unmein se shadi shuda hon aur jo shadi shuda na hon, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) (ke khandan ( ki aik londi ne zina kiya to aap ne mujhey hukm diya ke usey kode lagaaun, to achcha pata chala ke usey nifaas ( bachchey ki wilaadat se khoon aaney) ki haalat mein thoda hi arsa guzra tha. mujhey dar mehsus hua ke agar maine usey kode maarey to main usey mar daalun ga , chunanche maine Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se ye baat arz ki, to aap ne farmaya : tum ne achchha kiya."
4451,Israel ne suddi se isi sanad ke sath hadis bayan ki aur unhon-ne ye bayan kiya : jo unmein se shadi shuda hon aur jo shadi shuda na hon aur unhon-ne hadis mein ye izafa kiya is ( kaneez ( ko chhod do yahan tak ke wo sihat mand ho jaey.
4452,"Muhammad-bin-Jafar ne hamein hadis sunai, kaha : hamein Shoba ne hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine Qatada se suna, wo Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis bayan kar rahe they ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aik aadmi ko laya gaya jisne sharab pi thi, to aap ne usey khajoor ki do tahniyon se taqriban chalis (40) zarbein lagaaein . kaha : Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne bhi aisa hi kiya, jab Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ka zamana aaya, unhon-ne logon se mashwara liya to Hazrat Abdur-Rehman (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : hudood mein sabse halki had assi kode hai, chunanche Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne usi ka hukm saadir kar diya."
4453,"Khalid-bin-Haaris ne kaha : hamein Shoba ne hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : hamein Qatada ne hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo keh rahe they : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aik aadmi laya gaya. padhi. phir isi tarah bayan kiya."
4454,"Muaz-bin-Hisham ne kaha : mujhey mere walid ne Qatada se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne sharab mein khajoor ki tahni aur jooton se maara. phir Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne chalis (40) ( kode ( maarey , jab Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ka daur aaya aur log sar-sabz aur shaadaab maqamat aur bastiyon ke qareeb ja basey to unhon-ne ( mashwara kartey huey) puchha : sharab ki saza ke barey mein tumhari kya raey hai? to Hazrat Abdur-Rehman-bin-Auf (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : meri raey hai ke aap usey sabse halki had ke barabar muqarrar kar dein. kaha : iske baad Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne assi kode maarey."
4455,Yahya-bin-Saeed ne Hisham se isi sanad ke sath usi ki tarah hadis bayan ki.
4456,Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai janab Rasulullah ‌(sl) sharab mein chalis (40) mar maartey they tahniyon se aur jooton se. phir un donon ki hadis ki tarah bayan kiya aur unhon-ne sar sabz aur shaadaab maqamat aur bastiyon (ke qareeb basney) ka zikr nahi kiya.
4457,"Husain-bin-munzir se riwayat hai, main saiyedna Usman-bin-Affan (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas maujood tha Waleed-bin-Aqba (Raziallahu anhu) ko lekar aaey unhon-ne subah ki do rakatein padhein thin phir kaha : main zyada karta hun tumharey liye to do aadmiyon ne Waleed (Raziallahu anhu) par gawahi di. aik to Humran ne kaha isne sharab pi hai. doosrey ne ye gawahi di ke wo mere samney qai kar raha tha sharab ki. saiyedna Usman-bin-Affan (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : agar us ne sharab na pi hoti to qai kiyon karta sharab ki. saiyedna Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ne saiyedna Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ko kaha : utho isko had lagaao. (ye saiyedna Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ne saiyedna Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ki izzat aur azmat badhaney ke liye hukm diya aur imam ko ye Amr (baat) jaaiz hai). saiyedna Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne saiyedna Hasan (Raziallahu anhu) se farmaya : aey Hasan ! uth aur usko kode laga saiyedna Hasan (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : Usman khilafat ka sard ley chukey hain to garm bhi unhein par rakho . saiyedna Ali (Raziallahu anhu) is baat par ghussa huey saiyedna Hasan (Raziallahu anhu) par aur kaha : aey Abdullah-bin-Jafar ! uth aur kode laga Waleed (Raziallahu anhu) ko wo uthey aur Waleed (Raziallahu anhu) ko kode lagaey aur saiyedna Ali (Raziallahu anhu) gintey jatey they jab chalis (40) kode lagaey to saiyedna Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : bas theher ja phir kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne chalis (40) kode lagaey aur saiyedna Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne bhi chalis (40) lagaey aur saiyedna umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne assi lagaey aur sab sunnat hain aur mere nazdeek chalis (40) lagana behtar hai. Ali-bin Hujr ne apni riwayat mein izafa kiya : Ismail ne kaha : maine danaj ki hadis unse suni thi lekin usey yad nahi rakh saka."
4458,"Yazeed-bin-Zuree ne kaha : hamein Sufiyan Sory ne abu-Haseen se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Umair-bin-Sad se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : main kisi shakhs par had nahi lagata ke wo usmein mar jaey to main us se apne dil mein koi malaal mehsus karun siwaey sharab peeney waley ke. wo agar mar jaey to main uski diyat ada karunga kyonke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne is tareeqey (assi kodon ki saza ( ko jari nahi kiya."
4459,Abdur-Rehman ne Sufiyan se isi sanad ke sath usi ki tarah hadis bayan ki.
4460,Hazrat abu-Barda Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko ye farmatey huey suna : hududullah mein se kisi had ke ilawa kisi ko das se zyada kode na maarey jaaein.
4461,Ubada-bin-Samit (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath baithey they aap ne farmaya bait karo mujh se is iqrar par ke Allah Taala ka Sharik kisi ko nahi karengey aur zina aur chori aur nahaq khoon jis ko Allah Taala ne haram kya nahi karengey. phir jo koi apne iqrar ko pura karega uska sawab Allah Taala par hoga aur jo koi kaam unmein se kar baithega phir usko duniya mein uski saza milegi (yani had lagegi) to wahi uske gunah ka kaffara hai aur jo duniya mein Allah Taala uske kaam ko chipa ley to ( aaqibat mein) Allah Taala ko ikhtiyar hai chahey usko maaf kar de chahey azab de-dey.
4462,Mamar ne Zohri se isi sanad ke sath hadis bayan ki aur hadis mein ye izafa kya : iske baad aap ne hamarey samney aurton (ke ehkaam) wali (sura al-mumtahina ki) ye aayat tilawat ki : ke wo Allah ke sath kisi cheez ko Sharik na karein.
4463,"Abu Ashas sanaani ne Hazrat Ubada-bin-Samit (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ham se (isi tarah) ahad liya jis tarah aap ne aurton se ahad liya tha : ham Allah ke sath kisi ko Sharik na karengey, chori na karengey, zina na karengey, apni aulad ko qatl na karengey aur aik-doosrey par tohmat na lagaaengey : tum mein se jisne efaa kya uska ajr Allah par hai aur jisne aisa kaam kya jis par had hai aur usko had laga di gaee to wo uska kaffara hogi, aur jiska Allah ne parda rakha uska mamla Allah ke sipurd hai, agar chahey to usey azab de aur chahey to maaf kar de."
4464,"Qutaiba-bin-Saeed aur Muhammad-bin Rumeh ne Leis se, unhon-ne Yazeed bin abi Habib se, unhon-ne abul-Khair se, unhon-ne (Abdur-Rehman) Sunabihi se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Ubada-bin-Samit (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke unhon-ne kaha : main un naqeebon mein se hun jinhoney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki bait ki thi aur kaha : ham ne is baat par aap ke sath bait ki ke Allah ke sath kisi ko Sharik na karengey, zina na karengey, chori na karengey, kisi zinda ( insan ( ko nahaq qatl na karengey jisey Allah ne hurmat ata ki hai, daakey na daalengey aur nafarmani na karengey. agar ham ne is par amal kya to jannat hai aur agar ham ne inmein se kisi cheez ka irtikaab kya to uska faisla Allah ke sipurd hoga. ibne- Rumeh ne iska faisla ke bajaey us shakhs ka faisla izzat aur jalaal waaley Allah ke sipurd hoga kaha."
4465,Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai janab Rasulullah ‌(sl) ne farmaya : janwar ka zakhmi karna laghw hai (yani iska taawaan kisi par na hoga) ‌ aur kunwan laghw hai ‌ aur ‌Rikaz main panchwan hissey hai.
4466,ibne-Uena aur Imam Malik donon ne Zohri se Leis ki sanad ke sath usi ki tarah hadis bayan ki.
4467,"Yunus ne ibne-Shahab se, unhon-ne ibne-Musaiyab aur Ubaidullah-bin-Abdullah se, unhon-ne Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se usi ki tarah riwayat ki."
4468,"Aswad bin Alaa ne abu-Salma-bin-Abdur-Rehman se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke aap ne farmaya : kuwein ke zakhm par taawaan nahi, ( dhaat wghaira ki) kaan ke zakhm par taawaan nahi, chaupaaey ke zakhm (ya nuqsan ( par taawaan nahi aur dafeeney mein panchwan hissey hai."
4469,Muhammad-bin-Ziyad ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se usi ki tarah riwayat ki.
